
"Samantha!" He yelled.
"Johnny?" I was shocked. What was he doing? He ran up to me and the second he reached me, he crashed his lips onto mine. He lifted me off the ground.
"I love you. Move in with me." He said as he broke away. I looked down at him. That was a big step. But it was Johnny and I loved him.
"Yes." I said. "Yes a million times over." I said. Johnny smiled and kissed me again.